# ThirdwebSDK.getMultiwrap() method

> Warning: This API is now obsolete.
>
> This method is deprecated and will be removed in a future major version. You should use [getContract()](./sdk.getcontract.md) instead.
>
> ```diff
> - const multiWrap = await sdk.getMultiwrap("0x1234...");
> + const multiWrap = await sdk.getContract("0x1234...", "multiwrap");
> ```

Get an instance of a Pack contract

**Signature:**

```typescript
getMultiwrap(contractAddress: AddressOrEns): Promise<import("..").Multiwrap>;
```

## Parameters

| Parameter       | Type                                  | Description                          |
| --------------- | ------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| contractAddress | [AddressOrEns](./sdk.addressorens.md) | the address of the deployed contract |

**Returns:**

Promise&lt;import("..").[Multiwrap](./sdk.multiwrap.md)&gt;
